casebody.data:
Howard, Respondent, v. Langan et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and, County, General Term. November 12, 1890.) Appeal from city court, general term.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

M. J. Langan, for appellants. F. W. Judge, Jr., for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
